43:27.394 --> 43:29.658
We get you a passport then.

43:31.654 --> 43:32.928
Take a trip.

43:46.552 --> 43:49.251
Ain't easy civilizing
this motherfucker.

43:51.247 --> 43:52.872
We chose poorly, gus.

43:55.494 --> 43:59.152
At this rate, there won't be much
to call a newspaper in 10 years.

44:00.701 --> 44:03.376
You know, my father
worked over at armco, right?

44:04.407 --> 44:06.957
And every morning
before he went to work,

44:07.117 --> 44:08.709
he'd sit at the table,

44:08.903 --> 44:11.646
reading the newspaper
with a cup of coffee,

44:12.897 --> 44:14.712
and no one could interupt him

44:15.107 --> 44:17.734
for that 15 minutes
before he walked out the door,

44:19.598 --> 44:21.566
and I remember watching him, thinking,

44:21.805 --> 44:25.578
"What the hell is so important
about that damned paper?

44:27.353 --> 44:29.130
I want to be part of that."

44:30.728 --> 44:32.857
Made me want to be a newspaperman.

44:37.204 --> 44:40.030
One day I was cutting class
at Patterson,

44:40.673 --> 44:42.729
and there was this man
on the downtown bus

44:42.889 --> 44:45.108
folding his broadsheet just so.

44:48.231 --> 44:50.403
And the way that man folded that paper

44:50.854 --> 44:53.639
and concentrated on reading those pages

44:54.275 --> 44:57.296
made him look like the smartest
son of a bitch on the bus.

44:57.950 --> 45:00.078
It was just one of those moments.

45:06.779 --> 45:08.829
"If, ever I depart this vale,

45:09.586 --> 45:11.225
"and you ever remember me

45:11.385 --> 45:13.595
"and have thought to please my ghost,

45:15.152 --> 45:16.622
"forgive some sinner,

45:17.648 --> 45:20.197
"and wink your eye
at some homely girl."

45:21.101 --> 45:22.482
Fuck Henry Mencken.

45:27.732 --> 45:29.136
I forgive you, gus.

46:13.477 --> 46:14.991
Oh, my God.

46:17.121 --> 46:20.331
You see that quote from somebody
about me stabbing Burrell in the back?

46:21.291 --> 46:22.564
That's a damn lie.

46:22.848 --> 46:24.076
So what?

46:25.152 --> 46:27.606
You're going to be
named commissioner.

46:28.849 --> 46:31.992
This is good news.
How is this not good news?

46:41.485 --> 46:42.474
Thanks.

46:43.834 --> 46:45.633
Cheap motherfucker.

47:14.856 --> 47:16.217
No, no, see.

47:16.721 --> 47:19.951
If you stack it with the domestic beer,
then I won't know.

47:21.148 --> 47:23.371
Cut a blind man some slack, hear?

47:27.553 --> 47:29.947
- Y'all servin'?
- If you got some I.D. on you.

47:33.841 --> 47:34.799
Who was that?

47:35.520 --> 47:36.592
Little girl.

47:47.052 --> 47:49.814
- Cash is in the register.
- Fuck the register, old man.

47:54.121 --> 47:57.830
They all up in your shit.
They going after every damn thing.

47:58.442 --> 47:59.532
Do you hear me?

47:59.809 --> 48:01.147
We going to jail.

48:06.022 --> 48:09.116
Focus, motherfucker, focus!

48:10.323 --> 48:11.294
Look here.

48:12.094 --> 48:15.618
Back in the girdle ads
underneath the story about the-

48:16.474 --> 48:19.550
the school board approving
a name change for p.s. 114,

48:20.362 --> 48:23.436
it's--
it's Jimmy Mcnulty's ripper.

48:24.885 --> 48:26.493
You know why they call them homeless?

48:26.860 --> 48:29.813
Because they ain't got a pot to piss in,
and you know why they ain't got a pot?

48:30.370 --> 48:31.982
Because nobody gives a good fuck.

48:33.413 --> 48:36.660
Shake it for another day or two,
and then you're back in the rotation.

48:41.303 --> 48:42.817
You done with this stupid shit?

48:43.943 --> 48:46.488
Who the fuck do you need
to hear it from, Jimmy?

48:49.556 --> 48:52.086
You have to let Burrell know
that this isn't coming from you.

48:52.246 --> 48:53.377
That won't matter.

48:53.659 --> 48:55.433
After what he read today,
I'm the threat.

48:55.593 --> 48:56.866
Then you have to tell him

48:57.026 --> 48:59.259
that you won't take the job,
that you don't want his chair.

48:59.419 --> 49:00.761
And he believes me?

49:01.226 --> 49:03.964
The alternative is that he goes public
with what he knows,

49:04.124 --> 49:06.600
whatever he has about the old days.

49:07.017 --> 49:09.728
- He sat on it this long.
- You said yourself,

49:10.154 --> 49:13.892
he'd rather bury that file than to
embarrass the department on his watch,

49:14.052 --> 49:16.235
but if it's between you
and him surviving,

49:16.687 --> 49:18.749
what do you think he'll do then?

49:24.959 --> 49:28.660
How much could even be in that file?
An assets investigation?

49:28.907 --> 49:30.199
Some loose talk?

49:30.871 --> 49:33.401
It was so long ago.
Most of those guys have moved on.

49:33.746 --> 49:35.062
He only needs smoke.

49:35.847 --> 49:38.034
He doesn't even need fire
to drag you down,

49:38.194 --> 49:39.608
to drag me down.

49:39.961 --> 49:42.862
Everything that we have
worked so hard for.

49:44.551 --> 49:46.350
We've already lost enough.

49:54.157 --> 49:55.775
What other people Omar got?

49:58.295 --> 50:00.247
Cosucker the one got the trouble.

50:01.911 --> 50:03.615
No need for you to stand tall on it.

50:09.219 --> 50:10.832
It don't have to be messy.

50:10.993 --> 50:13.600
Ain't no other way.
I can see that.

50:26.986 --> 50:28.280
Where I find Omar?

50:38.024 --> 50:39.329
Where Omar at?

50:47.579 --> 50:49.070
You a tough old man.

51:15.386 --> 51:16.886
When word get to Omar,

51:17.558 --> 51:19.402
make sure he hear everything.

51:27.454 --> 51:29.442
We still ain't got no line on the man,

51:29.602 --> 51:31.270
and now he comin' at us.

51:31.430 --> 51:32.793
We gonna change up.

51:33.231 --> 51:36.069
Marlo got to move indoors.
The rest of us need to live on the run.

51:36.229 --> 51:37.969
Fucked-up plan, you ask me.

51:38.129 --> 51:39.602
Marlo wants Omar.

51:39.836 --> 51:41.548
What else you need to know?

51:45.329 --> 51:47.722
You making your move on Burrell,
and I don't blame you,

51:47.882 --> 51:50.136
and the thing is,
I can help with that.

51:50.418 --> 51:53.489
The ministers, Nerese,
black legislative caucus--

51:53.874 --> 51:57.064
- I can bring them around for you.
- Feel free.

51:57.494 --> 52:00.567
All I need is some help
with this grand jury nonsense.

52:01.129 --> 52:02.111
You go to Bond,

52:02.581 --> 52:04.661
- you tell Bond that--
- I can't help you with that.

52:04.821 --> 52:07.588
Story's been out all day,
and our phone isn't ringing.

52:08.054 --> 52:09.546
The ministers, Nerese, the caucus,

52:09.706 --> 52:11.621
they're willing
to live with Daniels apparently.

52:12.063 --> 52:13.338
Thanks anyway.

52:20.195 --> 52:22.132
Thinking you can cut Clay loose, huh?

52:23.346 --> 52:24.706
Thinking I'm done.

52:51.444 --> 52:52.409
Bonjour.

52:53.221 --> 52:54.537
Came to see my account.

52:55.242 --> 52:56.885
Vous parlez pas francais?

52:57.643 --> 52:58.937
Y'all got my money?

52:59.233 --> 53:00.838
Je ne parle pas anglais.

53:06.853 --> 53:07.761
This mine.

53:07.921 --> 53:09.637
- Y'all got my money.
- Oui, monsieur.

53:10.128 --> 53:11.818
J'ai juste besoin de ça.

53:13.469 --> 53:15.961
S'il vous plaît,
est-ce que je pourrais avoir le...

53:17.146 --> 53:18.177
ça.

53:19.075 --> 53:20.165
Merci.

53:22.130 --> 53:23.693
Identification,
s'il vous plait.

53:23.853 --> 53:24.778
What?

53:26.340 --> 53:27.546
- Ça.
- Yeah.

53:29.298 --> 53:30.219
Oui.

53:31.842 --> 53:32.852
Merci.

53:37.531 --> 53:38.997
OK, monsieur Marlo.

53:42.629 --> 53:45.152
So you string together
Barlow's murder

53:45.698 --> 53:49.303
and Cole's unconnected case and yours,
which is natural to begin with...

53:49.463 --> 53:52.685
Instant serial killer,
which I thought would get the brass

53:52.845 --> 53:54.849
to begin kicking out some money
to work real cases.

53:55.009 --> 53:56.063
Like Marlo.

53:56.326 --> 53:57.468
Like Marlo.

54:01.410 --> 54:03.706
Shit like this actually goes
through your fucking brain?

54:05.230 --> 54:07.472
If you don't want listen to me,
then listen to Lester.

54:07.632 --> 54:09.051
He has all the wisdom you need.

54:09.211 --> 54:12.131
Joke of it is, no one gives
a fuck about a serial killer,

54:12.291 --> 54:15.121
not unless he's carving up
some pretty coed or some shit.

54:15.564 --> 54:17.871
Sunpapers put the story
in their back pages.

54:18.031 --> 54:19.404
Eh, you fucked up.

54:19.620 --> 54:20.981
Yeah. Tell him.

54:21.528 --> 54:25.405
No. I mean, if you want to do it right,
a straight-up strangle's not enough.

54:26.398 --> 54:27.634
Not if it's some vagrant.

54:32.143 --> 54:33.722
Sensationalize it.

54:34.317 --> 54:36.951
Give the killer some fucked-up fantasy,

54:37.111 --> 54:39.298
something bad, real bad.

54:39.781 --> 54:41.865
It's got to grip the hearts and minds,

54:42.025 --> 54:44.372
give the people what they want
from a serial killer.

54:44.532 --> 54:47.031
- Lester, what the fuck?
- No. You're onto something.

54:47.974 --> 54:50.400
I only need a few weeks
to pull down Marlo Stanfeld.

54:50.560 --> 54:52.666
You fly this mess right,
you can give it to me.

54:53.443 --> 54:56.065
Who gives a damn
if we fake a couple murders

54:56.225 --> 54:57.851
that we're never gonna solve, huh?

54:58.559 --> 55:00.106
The dead men don't care.

55:00.535 --> 55:01.861
No one cares,

55:02.363 --> 55:03.811
but if it's gonna get the bosses

55:03.971 --> 55:05.798
to throw down
enough coin to do police work--

55:05.958 --> 55:08.141
I'm out.
I'm out of here.

55:15.083 --> 55:16.973
We got to give your killer a name.

55:17.499 --> 55:19.100
We have to kill again.

55:36.392 --> 55:38.370
Poppy, we've got to cook
one of these one night.

55:38.530 --> 55:40.743
- Yeah, right on.
- Nice little dinner.

55:41.951 --> 55:43.658
Omar, Omar, Omar!

55:46.184 --> 55:48.224
Hold on, hold on, hold on!

55:49.756 --> 55:51.553
All right, all right. Here you go.

55:52.315 --> 55:54.805
- Mañana, poppy. Tomorrow, OK?
- Tomorrow.

55:55.156 --> 55:56.713
Mana, poppy. No.

55:56.873 --> 55:58.166
Mana, Alexis.

56:36.559 --> 56:40.343
Hey, 'Naldo, cous got to find out
where they got honeynut, yo,

56:41.067 --> 56:43.918
if they expect us
to call this spit o' land home.

56:58.459 --> 56:59.863
Recibía una llamada.

57:01.142 --> 57:02.655
Tengo mala noticia.

57:05.951 --> 57:06.954
Qué pasó?

57:08.890 --> 57:10.389
Mataron a Butchie.

